  "body": "## ISSUE 1: The specific messages content is not shown as per the design on the chat preview if a user himself sends some content and checks it in the preview\r\n**Steps to reproduce:**\r\n1. Go to 1-1 or group chat\r\n2. Send a message that contains the following content and recheck the preview page after each listed content sending:\r\n -  Text\r\n  - Image \r\n  - image with text\r\n  - Reply\r\n  - Mention\r\n  - Pinned message\r\n\r\n**Actual result:**\r\nFor all cases the 'you' is not shown at the beginning of the preview if user sends messages himself and checks them\r\n\r\n1. Text: a message text is shown on the preview\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223500314-e03d629a-edec-4f3f-964e-3e39c2346fa0.png)\r\n2. Image: 'placeholder' message is shown on preview if the image is sent\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223498409-426c18d4-6fdf-4d8c-88f5-44f34aa940dd.png)\r\n3. Reply: just a text is shown \r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223498885-e15af9b8-e684-49a8-a19e-e31941f51d5e.png)\r\n4. Mention: the mentioned user is shown without '@' in the begging\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223498546-5681f53e-edb4-4d54-bad3-23e57d557f45.png)\r\n5. Pin a message: A content of a pinned message is not shown\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223498299-65e518aa-94b0-4e1a-bcbb-836990cdf0d5.png)\r\n\r\n**Expected result:**\r\nThe preview should be shown in format \"You <content>\" if a user sends the message yourself\r\n1. Text \r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223492481-735f9f82-8b41-4dab-aa2d-891a1e4c0e22.png)\r\n2. Image: The count of images is shown\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223492616-2ad35a1c-4a86-422a-8d77-bcdfed35dc09.png)\r\n3. Image with the text: The count of images and text is shown\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223501919-b9a7add1-eb2c-4669-b0d9-47e9d2c1f082.png)\r\n\r\n4. Reply: 'You replied: <text content>' is shown\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223492905-b47952d9-4f4e-412f-9758-9ba17fbda20e.png)\r\n5. Pinned: You pinned: <text content> is shown if the current last message is pinned by the current user\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223492792-c37a35c2-f229-44e5-98c1-5ebb7d65f001.png)\r\n6. Mention: the '@' is shown if a particular user is mentioned\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223493787-d5888d31-e282-4828-9d92-4e52e9052f9a.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
