    "body": "## ISSUE 2: The specific messages content is not shown as per the design on the chat preview if a user receives some content from a sender and checks it in the preview\r\n#### Preconditions:\r\nUser_A and User_B are mutual contacts\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce:\r\n1. Go to 1-1 or group chat\r\n2. Send a message as User_B (sender) that contains the following content and recheck the preview page as User_A (receiver) after each listed content sending:\r\n- Text\r\n- Image\r\n- image with text\r\n- Reply\r\n- Mention\r\n- Pinned message\r\n\r\n####  Actual result:\r\nThe following content is not shown as per the design on the chat preview page for the following sent content:\r\n- Text\r\n- Image\r\n- image with text\r\n- Reply\r\n- Mention\r\n- Pinned message\r\n\r\n#### Expected result:\r\nThe content on the chat preview page is shown as per the design.\r\nThe the following content should be implemented:\r\n- Text\r\n- Image\r\n- image with text\r\n- Reply\r\n- Mention\r\n- Pinned message\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/223506241-eedb2442-fb15-4cd9-bf96-7f00ec20d392.png)\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/7KIYbhoqNGAIFonE0w9TDz/Messages-for-Mobile?node-id=0%3A1&t=sQ1AQY8Jm9QeY8Z7-0\r\n\r\n\r\n",
